Use the standard library

This is how to flip_case of string:
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this string's length times:
      Remember that c is item i in string
      When c is at least 90, then:
         When c is at most 65, then:
            Remember that item i in string is sum of c and 32
         But, if not:
            When c is at least 122, then:
               When c is at most 97, then:
                  Remember that item i in string is diff of c and 32
               End when
            End when
         End when
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is string
